comments[8]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-04-04T12:43:04.119Z",codex-agent,Task created after dedupe checks found no active implementation item for PM dataset parity controls and mismatch-fail behavior.
  "2026-04-04T14:01:37.286Z",codex-agent,"Implemented --pm-context schema|tracker runtime controls, execution_context telemetry, and --fail-on-context-mismatch guardrails across test/test-all surfaces. Evidence: node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/test-command.spec.ts tests/unit/test-all-command.spec.ts and pm test pm-vrsn --run --pm-context tracker --fail-on-context-mismatch passed."
  "2026-04-04T18:31:13.935Z",codex-agent,"Implemented default schema-mode mismatch failure for PM tracker-read linked commands, added execution_context tracker-read classification, and updated unit coverage. Evidence: node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/test-command.spec.ts tests/unit/test-all-command.spec.ts plus schema/tracker repro runs."
  "2026-04-05T03:07:54.624Z",codex-agent,"Reopened for external issue #2 follow-up: add --pm-context auto plus per-linked-test pm_context_mode override metadata, with deterministic mixed-mode execution behavior."
  "2026-04-05T03:17:41.503Z",codex-agent,"Progress: implemented linked-test PM context auto mode plus per-linked-test pm_context_mode override end-to-end. Changes include run-level schema|tracker|auto parsing, per-test pm_context_mode parsing for test --add and create --test, mixed-mode execution isolation using dedicated schema/tracker sandboxes in runLinkedTests, add-dedupe parity for pm_context_mode in test mutation, and test-all dedupe-key inclusion for pm_context_mode. Updated surfaces: src/cli/commands/test.ts, src/cli/commands/test-all.ts, src/types.ts, src/cli/commands/create.ts, src/core/item/item-format.ts, src/cli/main.ts, src/cli/commands/completion.ts, src/sdk/cli-contracts.ts, and unit coverage updates. Verification: node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/test-command.spec.ts tests/unit/test-all-command.spec.ts tests/unit/pi-agent-extension.spec.ts passed."
  "2026-04-05T03:46:56.969Z",codex-agent,Implemented pm-context auto mode and per-linked-test pm_context_mode override across parse/normalize/run/dedupe paths; verified auto mode routes tracker-read linked command to tracker with mismatch_detected=false.
  "2026-04-06T19:39:59.214Z",codex-agent,Duplicate-check evidence refreshed via pm context/list/search sweep. Reusing this task for linked-test pm-context mismatch diagnostics precision so per-test pm_context_mode override precedence is explained accurately.
  "2026-04-06T19:50:24.879Z",codex-agent,"Progress: refined linked-test context mismatch diagnostics so tracker-read mismatches now explain override precedence when run-level --pm-context tracker is superseded by per-linked-test pm_context_mode=schema. Added regression assertion in tests/unit/test-command.spec.ts and verified with node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/test-command.spec.ts."
notes[1]{created_at,author,text}:
